Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Circus Festival will be held soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Circus Festival is a big\Ncompetition held every three years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in which the world's top\Nartists compete against each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}doing their really amazing techniques.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone has been training very hard for\Nthis date, betting everything they've got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla won the last\Ncompetition with the Golden Phoenix!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to be the real Kaleido Star\NMiss Layla charged me with becoming,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll fly all the way to where\Nyou are. I'll do it! I'll do it! I'll do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa \Naka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they've announced it,\Nthey've announced it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my name is \Nlisted, by any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they listed your name,\Nit would be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being nominated here \Nitself is very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora... Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not listed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name isn't listed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's name hasn't come up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you'd expect from the International\NCircus Festival held once every three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was tough to get in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a webpage for the\Ncompetition they did three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla and Yuri. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They won admirably in this\Ncompetition three years ago, didn't they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the performance they did at\Nthat time was the Golden Phoenix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winning at this festival was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this trophy will \Ngive me new strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength to jump higher and farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I wish I could say something\Ncool like that. I wish! I wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in order to do that,\NI have to be in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard and enter the\Nfestival together three years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to surpass Miss Layla, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to participate\Nin the Circus Festival too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, this is a part of my dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon's name is not listed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Leon's abilities,\Nhe'd definitely have been chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Amazing Training With Leon."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, when I was in New York--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all you did for me! Don't you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to appear on the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Salome in Vegas" is suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cathy, the director, caused\Ntrouble with the producer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the reason\NI came here today is for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invitations to participate\Nin the Circus Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're known as Phoenix Tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Layla won three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she has an unconditional "seed"\Nright to participate in the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's saying that she wants to\Nrecommend one of you in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recommend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean one of us can enter the Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will absolutely work hard.\NSo, please recommend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll work my hardest too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to work hard on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Circus Festival is not just a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place where participants\Nseriously compete with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place where they\Ncompete; win or lose, live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All participants compete,\Nbetting everything they've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The requirement is not only working\Nhard, but also the preparedness to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Participating in this\Nwith Layla's recommendation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means you'll be expected to produce\Nthe high-level results that implies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as members of Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if people see you making a\Nclumsy performance at the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will affect the size of\Nour audiences afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decide which of the two it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trapeze acts have\Nto be performed in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you'll be the other half of the pair,\Nyou have the right to choose your own partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you I would\Nparticipate in something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not ready to definitely win,\Nyou don't have to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\NI'm the one who's refusing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder, maybe, if you don't have the\Nconfidence to win in the Circus Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you have so many enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there are many on the\Nselection committee who hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the reason why you\Nwere not selected for this event
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because you've ended the\Ncareers of countless partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ended their careers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are some committee members\Nwho will want to keep the trophy from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if only out of stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a duel between you and your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Participate and win, or run\Naway now. One or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who decides, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A duel with fate... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, I had no choice but to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won my duel with fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran away then, if I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran away, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd entered, but you never\Nshowed up at the festival site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what reasons you had, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to aim for winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whichever one will end up\Nparticipating, I'll have to train her more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you may be destroyed. You're\Nprepared to take that chance, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't satisfy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how many people are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're destroyed, it means\Nthey weren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage is waiting for you. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you already know\Nwhat everybody calls Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Death. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're doing this, knowing\Nfull well what may come of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to win in the Circus Festival,\Nwe need that much preparedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who taught me that, Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're going to choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard so you don't feel\Nashamed of me as a partner in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a chance for you to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a perfect chance\Nfor you to show off in today's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much. I... I will do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, as I thought, Leon likes May better...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I still should have a chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saying he's destroyed countless\Npartners... I wonder what that meant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, May?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I screwed up something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you can't\Nhandle a little ad lib like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ad lib...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean you did it on purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible! Why would\Nyou do something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone has not reached the level\NI expect, that person is going to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're not called\Nthe God of Death for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on the festival and\Nheal that shoulder quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you destroy me because I was an eyesore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to blame something,\Nblame your lack of skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have time to\Nworry about somebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be\Ndestroyed by Leon as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should put forth more\Neffort than you have in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, you will\Nhave special training. Be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed the whole time, and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was May?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the ligament\Nin her right shoulder is torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she was told that\Nit would take a while to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have to suspend the\Nperformances of Dracula for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The God of Death." I heard it before too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever is paired with\NLeon always leaves the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you sure pairing\Nwith Leon is a good idea after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. If Sora is destroyed\Ntoo, the Kaleido Stage will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to play Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a chance for you to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a perfect chance\Nfor you to show off in today's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May... I wonder if she'll be all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy because \Nyour rival dropped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May worked so hard playing\NMina Murray as Mr. Leon's partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then he did something like that to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, if she finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking special training while \Nshe's suffering from her injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what she'll think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worrying about May?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you worried that you might be hated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As someone aiming to be a real Kaleido Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that so important to be troubled with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things I have to do right now are \Nto participate in the festival and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, I had no choice but to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won my duel with fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other path for me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to surpass Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be a true Kaleido Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what kind of special\Ntraining it is, I'll withstand it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be destroyed. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The training that you'll go\Nthrough will be very difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I say you can stop, stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But stand there with only your right foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all? That's the special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the special training\Nfor the legendary great maneuver was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you will find out how\Neasy that was in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets to be too much for you,\Nrun away whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away! I'll show you;\NI'll be your partner for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost three hours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was wondering just how\Namazing the special training was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's just telling her to stand there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this just harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be. After all,\NLeon is called the God of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it one more time from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have only two options: do it or quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't switch your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today it's the left foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What purpose is this going to serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon is probably trying\Nto hammer the basics home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, you used\Nto say she lacks the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sora, standing in the same position\Nfor a long time should be very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's hindering the\Nrange of her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Leon sees her weakness\Nand is trying to correct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if he overdoes it, he may\Nwell also kill her good points,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like her flexibility or the muscle power\Nshe can put forth starting from a standstill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think he's just\Ntrying to destroy Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're having \Nanother nice day today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, can you perform at Kids Stage today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of... course, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even yesterday, your timing was off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of this special \Ntraining, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll do my best. So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, the more I think about it, the more\NI think you should stop this special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, you're going to quit now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, I can't allow you to\Nkeep doing things like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to build up her basics,\NI will make a training menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do. Because, Sora is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see this through to the end, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let him say that the special training\Nfor the legendary great maneuver was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the girl from Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she made some kind\Nof mistake, and is being punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she did, it's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Leon thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than two hours
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since she started standing \Non one foot on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really doing anything for Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this girl? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's the first to ever endure this much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius's bow is drawn \Nto its utmost limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless she can shoot an arrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bowstring will snap, and \Neverything will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's reached her limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be painful for you to\Neven stand normally on those legs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you keep smiling? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, this isn't\Nbasic training or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think this is \Nfor the festival either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way I can see it is that he's just trying\Nto destroy Sora even if only out of stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, why are you overreacting so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing this because it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're afraid of Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't acknowledge May's skills,\Nyet you chose her as a partner
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're still at Kaleido Stage. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you seeking from Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is my dream, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you destroy her out of petty\Nstubbornness, I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The special training is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, she passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You don't need to do it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora! It's finished! It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did excellent, Sora. You passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Congratulations, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Afraid of her? Me? Impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's ridiculous. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand it!\NI really, really can't stand it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sekasu you ni muragaru Hard luck{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagasarete Time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokoku doori Take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsuredasu yo imasugu {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gouin only (saisoku drive) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nichijou miorosu best view {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asu no tame ni escape {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakansu nashi demo oashisu wa get{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keitai off tte ai o charge shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yasashisa dake ja iyasenai itami mo aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone. Surechigau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koukai no hate ni deau true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naite mo waratte mo I’ll be with U{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star: New Wings"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:24:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You talk pretty, but\Naren't you just running away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I passed! Or that's what\NI thought. Then, the final test?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's a very cruel one. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember now. I'll show \Nyou who I really am!{\i0}
